'''Conscript Academic Officer''' ([[Norwegian language|Norwegian:]] Vernepliktig akademisk befal (VAB)) is an arrangement by the Norwegian Military where academics within different professions (doctors, psychologists, pharmacists, dentists etc.) serve their conscription after completing their education.<ref>[http://www.mil.no/felles/fsan/start/article.jhtml?articleID=133066 mil.no: ''Klarere regler for akademisk befal''] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070805020947/http://www.mil.no/felles/fsan/start/article.jhtml?articleID=133066 |date=2007-08-05 }}</ref> They will then receive [[lieutenant]] ranking when they start their military service.

